                        <h2 class="mb-4 text-primary" data-aos="fade-up">Why use Turbo Tickets?</h2>

                        <p class="mb-0" data-aos="fade-up">
                            Turbo Tickets is a centralized issue tracker. It enables you to achieve a streamlined workflow by letting you create, update, archive and track work tickets. 
                            Turbo Tickets connects all the layers and stakeholders behind the scenes so that you can enjoy noise free navigation of a user friendly interface.
                            <br><br>
                            Other users can only join your company via invites. All access privileges are based on the roles you assign your team members.
                            Project updates are logged and the stakeholders are notified upon pre-defined actions.
                        </p>
                    </div>
